%N A168698 Number of reduced words of length n in Coxeter group on 21 generators S_i with relations (S_i)^2 = (S_i S_j)^17 = I.
%C A168698 The initial terms coincide with those of A170740, although the two sequences are eventually different.
%C A168698 First disagreement at index 17: a(17) = 13762559999999999999790, A170740(17) = 13762560000000000000000. - _Klaus Brockhaus_, Mar 30 2011
%C A168698 Computed with Magma using commands similar to those used to compute A154638.
%H A168698 G. C. Greubel, <a href="/A168698/b168698.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..500</a>
